the\nsystem size). Remarkably accurate estimates for the true distributions of\nviable reaction fluxes are obtained, suggesting that, although further\nimprovements are desirable, our method enhances our ability to analyze the\nspace of allowed configurations for large biochemical reaction networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2013 16:12:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-24"}
