 the scaling relations is consistent with the Salpeter\npower-law index.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2013 19:25:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2013 21:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-04"}
